phptools NEWS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Wed Aug 23, 2006:
	* 0.5 released
	* Added `phptools analyze-globals' to produce a report analyzing the
	  occurrence and reference of global variables in a source tree.
	* Lots of bug fixes to parser and scanner (still PHP4 only).

Fri Aug 11, 2006:
	* Project ressurected!

Wed Apr 17, 2002:
	* 0.1 released
	* Scanner and parser finished, phptools program written.

Mon Feb  4, 2002:
	* Project started.
